            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>erator</ex></expan> Caesar divi Nervae <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> N</supplied>erva Traia<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">nus <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustus</ex></expan> Germanicus pontife</supplied>x maximus <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>tribunic</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>potestat</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> c</supplied>o<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ul</ex></expan> II <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">equitibus et peditibus qui mil</supplied>itant in <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">alis duabus<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> et cohortibus qu</supplied>attuor <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">quae appellantur Frontoni</supplied>ana et I <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">civium Romanorum et I M</supplied>ont<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>no<lb break="no" n="8"/>[rum ------ </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ------ et sunt in] <lb n="2"/>Panno<supplied reason="lost">nia sub <expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aeo</ex></expan> Pinario Aemilio Cica</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>tricula P<supplied reason="lost">ompeio Longino item di</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>missis h<supplied reason="lost">onesta missione qui quina</supplied> <lb n="5"/>et vicen[a plurave stipendia meruerunt ------
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Fragment der tab. I. (B): Außenseite: AE 1982; Weber: Z. 6/7: [quae appellantur Sili]ana et I / [Augusta Ituraeorum et I M]ont[a]no/[rum ---]; Innenseite: Z. 3/4: AE 1982: P[ompeio Longino item di]missis fehlt; AE 1982; Weber: Z. 5: et vicen[a stipendia]. Datierung: Weber: Militärdiplom CIL 16, 00042 wurde unter demselben Statthalter am 20.2.98 ausgestellt; RMD: Ausstellung auch Anfang 99 möglich.</p>
